---
import Layout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<Layout title="VeloxOS - Privacy Policy">
    <main class="py-20 bg-white dark:bg-transparent transition-colors duration-300">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
            <div class="bg-slate-50 dark:bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm p-8 md:p-12 rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 dark:border-[#00b0f0]/15 shadow-xl dark:shadow-2xl">
                
                <div class="text-center mb-12">
                    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
                    <div class="w-16 h-1.5 bg-[#00b0f0] mx-auto rounded-full"></div>
                    <p class="mt-4 text-slate-500 text-sm uppercase tracking-widest">Commitment to Privacy-First Architecture</p>
                </div>

                <section class="mb-10">
                    <h2 class="text-[#00b0f0] text-xl font-bold border-l-4 border-[#00b0f0] pl-4 mb-4 uppercase tracking-wide">1. General Information</h2>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
                        The protection of your personal data is a high priority for us. This Privacy Policy informs you about how we handle data when you visit our website. As we aim for a <strong class="text-slate-900 dark:text-white">"privacy-first"</strong> approach, we collect as little data as possible.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <section class="mb-10 bg-[#00b0f0]/5 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-[#00b0f0]/10">
                    <h2 class="text-[#00b0f0] text-xl font-bold mb-6">2. Data Collection on our Website</h2>
                    <div class="grid gap-6">
                        <div>
                            <strong class="text-slate-900 dark:text-white block mb-2">Cookies:</strong>
                            <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">This website does not use tracking or marketing cookies. We only use essential technical cookies if they are strictly necessary for the website's functionality.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <strong class="text-slate-900 dark:text-white block mb-2">Comments & Accounts:</strong>
                            <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">We do not offer user accounts or comment sections, so no personal data is stored in this regard.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </section>

                <section class="mb-10">
                    <h2 class="text-[#00b0f0] text-xl font-bold border-l-4 border-[#00b0f0] pl-4 mb-4 uppercase tracking-wide">3. Server Log Files</h2>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed mb-6">
                        Our hosting provider (netcup GmbH) automatically collects and stores information in so-called server log files, which your browser automatically transmits to us:
                    </p>
                    <ul class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-3 text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">
                        <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-[#00b0f0]">ðŸ”¹</span> Browser type and version</li>
                        <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-[#00b0f0]">ðŸ”¹</span> Operating system used</li>
                        <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-[#00b0f0]">ðŸ”¹</span> Referrer URL</li>
                        <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-[#00b0f0]">ðŸ”¹</span> Host name of computer</li>
                        <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-[#00b0f0]">ðŸ”¹</span> Time of the server request</li>
                        <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-[#00b0f0]">ðŸ”¹</span> IP address</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p class="mt-6 text-xs text-slate-500 italic">
                        This data is required for technical reasons to ensure a stable and secure connection. Legal basis: Art. 6 (1) (f) GDPR.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <section class="mb-10 border-2 border-dashed border-[#00b0f0]/30 p-8 rounded-2xl bg-white dark:bg-transparent">
                    <h2 class="text-[#00b0f0] text-xl font-bold mb-4">4. ISO Downloads</h2>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
                        When you download a VeloxOS ISO file, the server may log the IP address and timestamp to ensure the integrity of our download mirrors and to prevent abuse. This data is not used to create personal user profiles.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <section class="mb-4">
                    <h2 class="text-[#00b0f0] text-xl font-bold border-l-4 border-[#00b0f0] pl-4 mb-4 uppercase tracking-wide">5. Your Rights</h2>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
                        You have the right to request information about your stored data at any time. You also have the right to request the correction, blocking, or deletion of this data. If you have questions, please reach out via the contact details in the imprint.
                    </p>
                </section>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-12 text-center">
                <a href="/" class="text-slate-500 hover:text-[#00b0f0] transition-colors text-sm font-medium">
                    &larr; Back to Homepage
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
</Layout>
